<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>에코가이드 - 맞춤형 분리수거 가이드</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="app-header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>🌱 에코가이드</h1>
            <p>우리 동네 맞춤형 분리배출 가이드라인</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="card step-section" id="step-location">
            <div class="step-badge">STEP 1</div>
            <h2>지역을 선택해주세요</h2>
            <div class="location-box">
                <button id="btn-gps" class="btn btn-primary">📍 현재 위치로 설정 (GPS)</button>
                <div class="divider">또는 직접 선택</div>
                <div class="select-group">
                    <select id="select-region">
                        <option value="">시/도 선택</option>
                        <option value="seoul">서울특별시</option>
                        <option value="gyeonggi">경기도</option>
                    </select>
                    <select id="select-district" disabled>
                        <option value="">시/군/구 선택</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="status-text" id="location-status">지역을 설정하면 해당 지자체의 가이드라인이 적용됩니다.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="card step-section disabled" id="step-category">
            <div class="step-badge">STEP 2</div>
            <h2>어떤 쓰레기인가요?</h2>
            
            <div class="category-tabs" id="category-tabs">
                </div>

            <div class="sub-category-box">
                <label for="select-trash-item">상세 항목 선택</label>
                <select id="select-trash-item" disabled>
                    <option value="">쓰레기 종류를 선택하세요</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card step-section disabled" id="step-condition">
            <div class="step-badge">STEP 3</div>
            <h2>쓰레기의 상태가 어떤가요?</h2>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label>오염도 체크</label>
                <div class="radio-group">
                    <label class="radio-label">
                        <input type="radio" name="contamination" value="clean" checked>
                        <span>깨끗함 (세척 완료)</span>
                    </label>
                    <label class="radio-label">
                        <input type="radio" name="contamination" value="dirty">
                        <span>이물질/오염 묻음</span>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="checkbox-label">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="check-mixed">
                        <span>테이프, 스티커, 라벨 등 다른 재질이 붙어있나요?</span>
                </label>
            </div>

            <button id="btn-analyze" class="btn btn-success btn-block">분리수거 방법 분석하기</button>
        </section>

        <section class="card step-section result-section hidden" id="step-result">
            <div class="result-header">
                <span class="badge" id="result-disposal-type">재활용</span>
                <h2 id="result-title">배달 떡볶이 용기</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="guide-box">
                <h3>💡 순차적 분리배출 가이드라인</h3>
                <ol class="guide-list" id="guide-steps">
                    </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="tip-box" id="result-tip-box">
                <strong>⚠️ 우리 동네(지자체) 특이사항:</strong>
                <p id="result-local-tip">해당 지자체는 목요일 대형 폐기물 수거일입니다.</p>
            </div>

            <button id="btn-reset" class="btn btn-secondary btn-block">처음부터 다시 찾기</button>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>©
